{"tid":1987104,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅志祥開直播賣食品遭網狂罵渣男30秒 一臉莫名其妙","createTime":"2020-04-24T08:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T09:55:24.000Z","uid":253829,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba5fc1d44927ca044997d3a481f2ba3a01844f24","tid":1987104,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T08:59:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://news.pchome.com.tw/newsdata/entertainment/nownews/20200424/58770756904949207006_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pchome.com.tw%2Fnewsdata%2Fentertainment%2Fnownews%2F20200424%2F58770756904949207006_1.jpg&h=067a6cff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://news.pchome.com.tw/newsdata/entertainment/nownews/20200424/58770756904949207006_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.pchome.com.tw%2Fnewsdata%2Fentertainment%2Fnownews%2F20200424%2F58770756904949207006_2.jpg&h=88f56b1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「南寧羅志祥」開直播賣食品，卻遭誤認成羅志祥（右圖）本尊，遭網友罵翻。（圖／翻攝臉書、羅志祥IG）<br />\n<br />\n周揚青昨（23）日在微博、IG宣布與羅志祥9年徹底情斷，甚至公開羅志祥劈腿、偷吃、約妹，以及兄弟大玩「多人運動」等行為，不僅重創羅志祥形象，也在演藝圈投下一顆震撼彈。而網友發現「羅志祥」於昨晚開直播，沒想到網友卻留言灌爆，狂罵「渣男」，後來網友才發現這人只是長得像羅志祥，並非本尊，鬧了一場烏龍。<br />\n<br />\n因為羅志祥爆發醜聞，所以與羅志祥有關的任何消息都會引起關注。先前羅志祥曾與南寧一名賣米的老闆撞臉，老闆名為蒙俊源，這位小哥也因為外型酷似羅志祥，因此受封「南寧羅志祥」，他本名是而他昨晚開直播，沒想到卻被網友們留言狂罵，激動留言「渣男」，或是揚言拒買，讓他被罵得一臉莫名其妙。<br />\n<br />\n到了後來終於有人發現罵錯人，紛紛留言：「你大哥出事了」、「南寧羅志祥扛下了所有」、「長得像羅志祥錯了嗎」。"},{"pid":"e4008415fed899137e3e44c5ccca13d3887cb897","tid":1987104,"uid":39215,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:00:44.000Z","msg":"靚仔過小豬好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f438b2b590e3aff4c4ba0d2d763bf9d90013d8f","tid":1987104,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:01:20.000Z","msg":"說什麼呢"},{"pid":"706637a586bf0faabad04036eaf1db650b4f52b7","tid":1987104,"uid":58630,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:01:29.000Z","msg":"似Tommy喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34986e65e78beea6646d20d9b5bd16f6e771941e","tid":1987104,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:01:35.000Z","msg":"乜野人就用乜野apps<br />\n冇乜好出奇"},{"pid":"d2d4c6735d66b9421bb449b4086087967480e6db","tid":1987104,"uid":128179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:02:34.000Z","msg":"有無人去埋舒韋恩史迪加到罵？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21a7688ce9dc552d0ff8cd2745bf40ca0bb0e39c","tid":1987104,"uid":21526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:19:20.000Z","msg":"屌笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca5cfce0162488df2c04f6bb54f8e55eddf2fcc","tid":1987104,"uid":144883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T09:55:24.000Z","msg":"「你大哥出事了」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}